  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/opentelemetry-instrumentation-celery-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 60183fb6242592c956864d7c6d477d63e4cb4062d565d0870c5928cf50b4c045
